name: E L E M E N T S V2

metadata.name: s p i r i t
metadata.description:
The element of spirit goes by several names, one of them is ether.

Instead of being invaders of nature, consuming all that she gave us and taking it for granted,
could we humans, with the help of technology that we created, 
be the protectors of nature with all her creatures included?

And even though she can live without us, better yet, she would flourish without us...
we are the ones who cannot live without her!
